# VolunteerCalendar — Complete Status & Outstanding Items

**Last Updated**: March 17, 2026
**Status**: MVP complete, deployed to volunteercalendar.org, pre-beta

---

## What's Built & Deployed

### Core App (Phases 1–6)
- Next.js 16 + TypeScript + Tailwind v4 + Firebase (Auth + Firestore)
- Full auth flow: login, register, password reset, welcome email
- Landing page with waitlist, sections: hero, pain points, how-it-works, features, pricing, footer
- Dashboard with sidebar nav, mobile drawer, getting-started wizard
- Church setup wizard (org type, name, timezone, workflow mode) with dynamic labels per org type
- Volunteer management: manual add, CSV import, profiles
- Ministry CRUD with color picker
- Service configuration (day, time, role slots)
- Scheduling algorithm with conflict detection, fair distribution
- Draft matrix view with manual overrides
- Ministry review workflow (Centralized Mode 1)
- Publish flow → email notifications → volunteer confirm/decline via token link
- Calendar feeds (iCal .ics) for Google/Outlook/Apple
- Dashboard analytics: fill rates, response rates, equity view
- CSV/JSON export + print-to-PDF
- Stripe billing: checkout, customer portal, webhook, tier gating (5 tiers: Free, Starter $19, Growth $49, Pro $99, Enterprise custom)

### Membership & Multi-Org (Phases 7a–7d)
- Membership data model with role-based permissions (owner, admin, scheduler, volunteer)
- Invite system: admin sends invite email → invitee accepts
- Self-registration: volunteer joins via public link → admin approves
- Org switcher for users in multiple churches
- Role-conditional navigation (admin vs volunteer views)
- Volunteer self-service portal: my-schedule, my-availability (blockout dates, weekly unavailable days), my-orgs
- Events system with open signup, role slots, recurring events

### Landing Page & Content (Phase 8)
- Inclusive language refresh (works for churches, nonprofits, any volunteer org)
- Warm editorial brand: DM Serif Display + DM Sans, indigo/coral/sage/sand palette
- Configurable org terminology (church/organization/team)

### Integrations (Phase 9)
- Planning Center, Breeze, Rock RMS import adapters
- Dashboard import UI with credential management

### Notifications & Reminders (Phase 10)
- 48h + 24h reminder emails via Resend
- SMS infrastructure via Twilio (pending toll-free verification)
- Per-volunteer reminder preferences (email, SMS, both, none)
- Admin notification center with send + history
- Lifecycle emails: purchase thank-you, re-engagement, upsell

### Account & Settings (Phase 11a)
- Legacy account membership auto-repair (accounts created before Phase 7 get owner membership on login)
- Settings page: profile editing (display name, password change)
- Settings page: organization settings (name, type, timezone) for admins
- Account deletion with confirmation for owners
- Firestore security rules bootstrap rule for initial org + membership creation

### Beta Hardening (Phase 11b)
- Favicon + PWA manifest (calendar icon, installable standalone app)
- Vercel Cron for daily automated reminders
- Error boundaries (global + dashboard-scoped)
- Custom 404 page
- SEO: robots.txt, sitemap.ts
- Privacy Policy and Terms of Service pages
- Mobile responsive audit across all dashboard pages
- Vercel Analytics + Speed Insights
- OG preview image (server-rendered)
- Test email endpoint for admins
- All emails route replies to info@volunteercal.com
- HarpElle attribution in footer

