## Environment Variables Reference

When switching from test to live mode, update in **both** `.env.local` and **Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables**:

| Variable | Current State | Action |
|----------|--------------|--------|
| `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY` | Test (`sk_test_...`) | Replace with `sk_live_...` |
| `STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET` | Test (`whsec_...`) | New secret from live webhook |
| `STRIPE_PRICE_STARTER` | Test price ID | New ID from live product |
| `STRIPE_PRICE_GROWTH` | Test price ID | New ID from live product |
| `STRIPE_PRICE_PRO` | Test price ID | New ID from live product |
| `RESEND_API_KEY` | Active (harpelle.com domain) | Keep; verify volunteercal.com later |
| `TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID` | Set | Keep |
| `TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN` | Set (regenerated March 17) | Keep |
| `TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER` | Set (toll-free, pending verification) | Keep |
| `CRON_SECRET` | Set | Keep |
| Firebase keys (`NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_*`) | Production | No change needed |

